      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 AP2 is a preserved masterclass in precision engineering. Powered by the high-revving F22C1 inline-four featuring VTEC variable valve timing, it delivers linear power up to its 8,200 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp, short-throw six-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque bias. The chassis is in exemplary state, retaining all 10 original VIN tags and showcasing a pristine undercarriage with zero oxidation. With its longitudinal front-mid engine layout and perfect 50/50 weight distribution, this S2000 provides an unadulterated analog driving experience. A rare, unmodified example in showroom condition.",
